Chuks Okocha in Abuja Sokoto State governor and Chairman, People’s Democratic Party (PDP) Governors Forum, Aminu Waziri Tambuwal, has stepped down for former Vice President Atiku Abubakar. Tambuwal who announced this at the ongoing National Convention at the Moshood Abiola Stadium in Abuja, urged all his delegates to vote for Atiku in national interestDetails later…